510
00:30:01,929 --> 00:30:04,630
melihat salinan banding?

511
00:30:06,929 --> 00:30:08,829
Bukan aku, Yang Mulia.

512
00:30:09,029 --> 00:30:10,870
Aku pun tidak tahu

513
00:30:11,740 --> 00:30:13,599
siapa dalang di balik insiden ini.

514
00:30:20,210 --> 00:30:21,310
Dal Moon.

515
00:30:21,310 --> 00:30:23,510
Aku mengikuti Pangeran Mil Poong selama ini.

516
00:30:24,779 --> 00:30:28,189
Aku tahu dia sedang memojokkan Istana Putra Mahkota.

517
00:30:29,389 --> 00:30:30,420
Benarkah itu?

518
00:30:31,560 --> 00:30:32,820
"Pemerintahan perwakilan".

519
00:30:36,159 --> 00:30:38,659
Untuk melengserkan Putra Mahkota dengan itu?

520
00:30:49,239 --> 00:30:50,469
Lantas kenapa

521
00:30:51,939 --> 00:30:53,409
