522
00:30:55,409 --> 00:30:58,120
Kenapa kamu tidak mengabari Istana Putra Mahkota?

523
00:31:02,019 --> 00:31:03,019
Godaan.

524
00:31:06,060 --> 00:31:07,659
Aku mungkin telah terpancing lagi

525
