541
00:32:07,220 --> 00:32:08,989
Ya, Putra Mahkota selalu memercayai

542
00:32:10,389 --> 00:32:11,760
semua ucapanku.

543
00:32:14,989 --> 00:32:16,130
Apa aku akhirnya

544
00:32:17,790 --> 00:32:19,730
bisa memenuhi keinginanmu?

545
00:32:26,839 --> 00:32:27,899
Benar.

546
00:32:29,109 --> 00:32:30,510
Bukan Min Jin Heon.

547
00:32:32,079 --> 00:32:34,339
Dia pun sama terkejutnya seperti aku.

548
00:32:36,609 --> 00:32:39,119
Kamu yakin tidak ada yang janggal

549
00:32:39,280 --> 00:32:40,579
dengan Pangeran Mil Poong?

550
00:32:40,619 --> 00:32:41,649
Ya,

551
00:32:42,619 --> 00:32:43,720
tidak ada.

552
00:32:45,119 --> 00:32:47,589
Dia hanya pergi ke rumah bordil dan minum-minum.

553
00:32:49,690 --> 00:32:50,690
Dal Moon.

554
00:32:52,799 --> 00:32:54,429
Dia tidak mungkin salah.

555
00:32:56,429 --> 00:32:58,170
