00:33:20,489 --> 00:33:22,359
Kenapa keadaan menjadi seperti ini?

565
00:33:22,959 --> 00:33:24,290
Ada apa ini?

566
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:27,600
Maafkan aku.

567
00:33:33,170 --> 00:33:34,299
Tuan Mun Su.

