00:34:49,109 --> 00:34:50,280
Ya.

590
00:34:51,410 --> 00:34:52,780
Pemerintahan perwakilan?

591
00:34:53,449 --> 00:34:55,489
Posisi Anda dan grup kami belum memiliki kuasa.

592
00:34:55,489 --> 00:34:56,590
Bagaimana mungkin kami melakukan itu?

593
00:34:57,290 --> 00:34:59,189
