654
00:39:00,030 --> 00:39:01,429
Itukah maksudmu?

655
00:39:08,670 --> 00:39:09,870
Apa kesalahan dia?

656
00:39:11,740 --> 00:39:13,079
Kenapa Putra Mahkota

657
00:39:14,010 --> 00:39:16,849
